'll not only be able to get exp faster with an enchantbot &quot;powerleveling&quot; you with charm but you'll also be able to fight in places that are just too risky alone. Summoners will also be no problem since you'll be able to kill anything thats mezable (or stunable). <br>
<br>
Another good partener is a bard. Like the enchanter brings alot of versitility and can be quite fun. Only drawback is at 65 you won't be able to benefit from the high exp of charm killing so in the end you'd loose out a bit with a bard. However bards can make quading alot easier with their speed and manasong so if you perfer quading to charm killing that might do it for you.<br>
<br>
